title: EQUIST (Equitable Impact Sensitive Tool)
slug: A platform by UNICEF to facilitate decision makers' development of equitable strategies to improve health and nutrition of the women and children in most vulnerable situations.
content: My responsibilties - Created dashboard, scenario analysis and user authentication on Angular framework, worked on CMS setup for admin in CakePhp and handled complex queries for database management.

type.title: UNICEF project for vulnerable women and children.

title: SAFER ROADS (City Intervention In India)
slug: An initiative led by AB InBev (Anheuser-Busch InBev) to make Gurugram's roadways safer through data-driven initiatives and constructive behavioral change.
content: My responsibilties -  Built dashboard to analyze road accidents and fatalities in black spots of India and integration of highcharts and google maps for demonstrating data.

type.title: Saferroads to analyze data to prevent accidents

title: UN INFO (UNDP)
slug: An online planning, monitoring and reporting system that digitizes each UNDAF/UNSDCF and the Joint work plans that go with them.
content: My responsibilities - Management of dashboard including complicated module development and enhancement of application using JS and JQuery.
